      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## Conclusion\n",
        "- Vanilla RNN learns short patterns but struggles with memory.\n",
        "- LSTM captures long-range dependencies better.\n",
        "- GRU provides similar performance with faster training.\n",
        "- Multiple corpora demonstrate sequence modeling across different styles.\n"
      ]
    }
  ]
}